Welcome to the HK Bushman Kitchen!

We are a Hong Kong group who would like to share our passion for bushcraft and culinary by demonstrating different kinds of Chinese and other styles of dishes unimaginable to be recreated in the wild.
We upload every other week, if not we will put up a short interesting video. Please enjoy!
